# Pangolin Provider

The **Pangolin** provider allows you to manage resources in [Pangolin](https://github.com/fosrl/pangolin), an open-source self-hosted tunneling and reverse proxy solution.

Use this provider to automate the lifecycle of organizations, sites, resources, roles, users, API keys, and OLM client devices via Infrastructure as Code.

